high_descs: Turn right and walk to the white door, then turn right and walk to the counter with the toaster on it.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge, in front and to the left of the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Take a step right and face the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and hang another right to walk to the counter where the toaster is.
Pick up a potato from next to the toaster.
Turn left to walk to the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn right to walk to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato in the fridge to put in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the counter to the counter on the left of the toaster.
Pick up the potato behind the tea kettle from the counter.
Turn around and go to the front go the refrigerator on the right.
Remove the potato after cooling it on the middle shelf inside the refrigerator.
Move over right to the microwave on the counter next to the refrigerator.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled potato in the microwave.
